SCOPE & STOP Hormones Analysis

37.2 SCOPE vs STOP

Fit LME models for Prolactin, HPL and GH2.
Fit GEE models for Insulin and HOMA-IR.

  • Outcomes: Prolactin, hPL, GH2, Insulin, HOMA-IR, Glucose (all outcomes log-transformed)
  • Independent variables: Study, GA at sampling
  • Model fitted: LME or GEE model
          log(hormones) ~ Study + GA at sampling + Study:GA at sampling
          LME only: Random intercepts for Study ID and Plate
          GEE only: Independence correlation structure
